name: pgVZ
description:
This is a Stable Diffusion textual inversion about a modern era celebrity. If you wanna test it, you can put this word on the prompt: pgVZ.

PS: The test images was made with 'vainilla' SD 1.5 model. The last one I keep because I like its imperfection. I don't know if works on SD 2.1 .
